                    An individual whose annual household income is R 50,000 or less.

                </p>
                <p class="description">
                    3S IT TRAINING provides free-of-cost computer, Basic Computers and related training to underprivileged children and youth at its centers. 3S IT TRAINING endeavors not only to improve knowledge of students but also enhance employability of youth population.
