                    Promoting Education is the focus of CSR and following are the activities:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <h3>Supporting skill development</h3>
                        <p class="description">
                            Providing computer and related literacy to underprivileged children and youth, including high school and college drop-outs, at 3S IT TRAINING Centers.
                        </p>
                        <p class="description">
                            The entire fee of the course will be borne by 3S IT TRAINING and its subsidiaries.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <h3>Empowering through education</h3>
                        <p class="description">
