                <h2>Execution of CSR Activity</h2>
                <p class="description">
                    Promoting Education is the focus of CSR and following are the activities:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <h3>1.   Supporting skill development</h3>
                        <ul>
                            For supporting skill development:
                            <li>
                                <p class="description">
                                    HR would engage with NGOs which are working in area of skill development and would provide details related to course, fee and center location to NGOs.
                                </p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p class="description">
                                    Once the course and the location of the center is decided by the NGO, it would share the list of students along with course details and center location with HR.
                                </p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p class="description">
                                    Operations would create separate fee plan for CSR.
                                </p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p class="description">
                                    Names of students would be entered in “3S IT TRAINING” under CSR fee plan.
                                </p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p class="description">
                                    NGO would share the invoice in name of 3S IT TRAINING AND BUSINESS SOLUTIONS. The invoice would include the course fee plus an additional 10%. This additional 10% is against the expenses that NGO would have incurred for administration and the related activities for mobilizing the students for the course.
                                </p>
                            </li>

                        </ul>


                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <h3>2.   Empowering through education</h3>
                        <ul>

                            <li>
                                <p class="description">
                                    Engaging with NGOs which are working in area of education.
                                </p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p class="description">
                                    Providing financial assistance to NGOs, so that the NGOs can facilitate the development of children and youth through imparting knowledge and skills through predefined channels.
                                </p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
